    "description": "Zostel Asia Pacific Associates, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Category Manager for our Dhanbad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Zostel Asia Pacific Associates:\nZostel Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zostel Asia Pacific Associates!",
